{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1781761793286,"sessionID":"ses_126b933ddffe3XZ7heot3Sz6EF","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"mk-spec-memory_memory_match_triggers","callID":"call_1ExT9k97c5YdypRCKZKbyNVS","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"prompt":"You are a deep-review agent running a fan-out lineage.\n\nRead .opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/deep-review/SKILL.md and execute the review loop with these parameters:\n  spec_folder: .opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/005-verification-and-remediation/006-deep-review-017-021-remediation/review-r2/scopes/B-rest-of-002\n  config.fanout_lineage_artifact_dir: /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/005-verification-and-remediation/006-deep-review-017-021-remediation/review-r2/lineages/gpt55r2-b-3\n  session_id: fanout-gpt55r2-b-3-1781761339355-o7qylx\n  executor: cli-opencode model=openai/gpt-5.5-fast\n  loop_type: review\n  config.maxIterations: 1\n\nThe step_resolve_artifact_root step will bind artifact_dir to /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/005-verification-and-remediation/006-deep-review-017-021-remediation/review-r2/lineages/gpt55r2-b-3 via the\nconfig.fanout_lineage_artifact_dir override — do NOT run the resolveArtifactRoot node\ncommand; bind artifact_dir directly to the override value.\n\nRun phase_init, phase_main_loop (to convergence OR config.maxIterations, whichever comes first), and phase_synthesis.\nWrite all outputs to /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/005-verification-and-remediation/006-deep-review-017-021-remediation/review-r2/lineages/gpt55r2-b-3. Do not touch any path outside /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/005-verification-and-remediation/006-deep-review-017-021-remediation/review-r2/lineages/gpt55r2-b-3.\n\nWhen complete, output a single line: FANOUT_LINEAGE_COMPLETE:gpt55r2-b-3","specFolder":".opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/005-verification-and-remediation/006-deep-review-017-021-remediation/review-r2/scopes/B-rest-of-002","tenantId":"","userId":"","agentId":"","limit":5,"session_id":"fanout-gpt55r2-b-3-1781761339355-o7qylx","turnNumber":1,"include_cognitive":false},"output":"{\n  \"summary\": \"Error: sessionId \\\"fanout-gpt55r2-b-3-1781761339355-o7qylx\\\" does not match a server-managed session. Omit sessionId to start a new server-generated session and reuse the effectiveSessionId returned by the server.\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"error\": \"sessionId \\\"fanout-gpt55r2-b-3-1781761339355-o7qylx\\\" does not match a server-managed session. Omit sessionId to start a new server-generated session and reuse the effectiveSessionId returned by the server.\",\n    \"code\": \"E_SESSION_SCOPE\",\n    \"details\": {\n      \"requestedSessionId\": \"fanout-gpt55r2-b-3-1781761339355-o7qylx\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"hints\": [\n    \"Omit session_id to start a new server-generated session, or reuse the effectiveSessionId returned by memory_context.\"\n  ],\n  \"meta\": {\n    \"tool\": \"memory_match_triggers\",\n    \"tokenCount\": 227,\n    \"cacheHit\": false,\n    \"isError\": true,\n    \"severity\": \"error\",\n    \"tokenBudget\": 3500\n  }\n}","metadata":{"truncated":false},"title":"","time":{"start":1781761785950,"end":1781761793283}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_0c1d0e1f208aadcd016a3386ee2d4c81918296021b1e1b67a2"}},"id":"prt_ed947126e001Ls6p8DTOLMVE6O","sessionID":"ses_126b933ddffe3XZ7heot3Sz6EF","messageID":"msg_ed946d0e0001pkgXdwM36CCY65"}}
