{"type":"text","timestamp":1781761930312,"sessionID":"ses_126b933ddffe3XZ7heot3Sz6EF","part":{"id":"prt_ed9495dc1001joJrQk3aZNsZjU","messageID":"msg_ed9493cf4001T1nFeARNUDp0aa","sessionID":"ses_126b933ddffe3XZ7heot3Sz6EF","type":"text","text":"The retention code intentionally switches to a purgeable-tombstone partition when `SPECKIT_SOFT_DELETE_TOMBSTONES=true`; I’m checking the test contract so I don’t report an intended two-stage delete as a defect.","time":{"start":1781761924546,"end":1781761930310},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_05e79933bcf547ab016a33878487348191ba9069c519b4a4bc","phase":"commentary"}}}}
